title: Barkers Building Supplies
description:
A shop selling all manner of DIY, electricals, decorating, plumbing and building materials, and general household goods.  Unusual in that almost everything is stored behind a counter - you ask, and the staff go and find things (this used to be a common shop format but is now only seen very occasionally in the UK).  It's quite a treasure trove - there's a huge amount and variety of stock in a rather small shop - and its rare to find something they don't stock.

8 Queenstown Road, London, SW8 3RX - Tel: 020 7622 0122
